bid(uint256).details: Places a bid on an NFT in the auction.When new highest bidder bids old bidders funds are automatically sent back easier for in contract accounting and they can rebid.

params.Id: The ID of the NFT being bid on.

params._nft: The address of the NFT contract.
params._nftIds: An array of NFT IDs to be auctioned.
params._paymentReceiver: The address of the payment receiver/seller.
params._startingBids: An array of starting bids for the NFTs.

end().details: Function for the auction to end.

start().details: Function for the auction to start.
